 .
 This package is part of KDE4, as a component of the KDE4 utilities module.
 See the 'kde' and 'kdeutils' packages for more information.


Package: ktimer
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: timer utility for KDE4
 This is a timer application for KDE4. It allows you to execute commands after
 a certain amount of time. It supports looping commands as well as delayed
 command execution.
 .
 This package is part of KDE4, as a component of the KDE4 utilities module.
 See the 'kde' and 'kdeutils' packages for more information.


